name: Cuteness Overload (Regenbow)
description: Welcome to "Cuteness Overload," where you are thrown into a farm of adorable creatures. Your mind is slowly being consumed by the sheer cuteness of the animals around you. With each passing moment, your sanity dwindles as the cuteness intensifies. To regain your sanity, you must take action and eliminate as many cute creatures as possible. But beware, this is not an easy feat. The more animals that remain alive, the stronger the cuteness becomes and the more challenging it is for you to reclaim your sanity. Will you be able to overcome the cuteness and restore your mind, or will you succumb to the overload and lose your sanity? Find out in "Cuteness Overload."
